description.en:
ETHVault is a 23.3% SurgeEth and 3.5% SafeVault rewarding token with a buy fee of 5% and a sell fee of 30%. 20% of the Sell fee gets distributed back to all the holders as SurgeEth every 12 from when they buy in and automatically and SafeVault as a manual claim.

Our biggest whale at Launch was SurgeEths Burn wallet which also accumluates SurgeEth Rewards. So we are constantly burning and buying SurgeEth.
